data.shortDescription: A contemporary bath faucet that fits in all spaces. Perfect for creating a cozy powder room atmosphere.
A modern goose neck bath faucet that transforms your master ensuite into an open, modern bath space.
A vessel faucet with a high-arc spout that provices plenty of sink room for any bathroom size.
An easy to control hand-operated showerhead that helps save time and energy by directing water exactly where you need it.
A luxurious showerhead that makes it rain from above, offering a unique and superier shower experience, all in the comfort of your own home bath.
